.SH "NAME"
systemd.syntax \- General syntax of systemd configuration files
.SH "INTRODUCTION"
.PP
This page describes the basic principles of configuration files used by
\fBsystemd\fR(1)
and related programs for:
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
